item.title: PyCon TW: Revisiting PythonPH's Journey Through New Eyes
item.description: Speaking at PyCon TW, Mickey and I reminisced on PythonPH's journey. The event also brought back the feelings we had in our 2012 PyCon experience, only now, through the unique lens as a community organizer.
